=== Server setup

0. apt-get update
1. bash -C "`wget -O - babushka.me/up`"
2. babushka alovak:'user setup'
3. babushka alovak:'rvm installed'
4. babushka alovak:'rails project'

on local machine
5. cap deploy:setup
6. cap deploy:check
7. cap deploy:update_code
7. cap deploy:migrate
8. cap db:seed
7. cap deploy

